org.puredata.core.utils

Class PdDispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.puredata.core.utils.PdDispatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PdReceiver

    public abstract class PdDispatcher
extends Object
implements PdReceiver
    PdDispatcher is an implementation of PdReceiver that dispatches messages from Pd to instances of PdListener based on the Pd symbol they originate from. Instances of this class automatically handle subscriptions to Pd symbols.
    Author:
    Peter Brinkmann (peter.brinkmann@gmail.com)
